data.description: Beautiful remodeled single family home featured in the quiet subdivision of Lindon Park located in Tempe, AZ. This home incorporates a subtle balance of both contemporary finishes with a modern design. The home features 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, 1,260 sqft [open concept] floor plan while featuring an upgraded kitchen boasting quartz countertops, shaker cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and eat-in island. Additional features would include a new HVAC system, dual pane [low-e 340] windows, spacious living space, wood look plank tile flooring, modern plumbing/lighting fixtures, ceiling fans, dual pane [low-e] windows, upgraded baths, new exterior doors, and plenty of natural light throughout the home. Lastly, the home features a detached 2-car tandem garage w/ upgraded epoxy coating floors, a large private backyard retreat featuring zero-scape desert landscaping, RV Gate, and covered patio space--perfect for entertaining guests & family. Home is in close proximity to walking & bike paths, green spaces, ASU, Tempe Marketplace, and south Scottsdale--don't miss your opportunity to call this home!
